#################################
######## Account one     ########
#################################

IMAPAccount one
Host imap.one.com
User steen@hegelund-hansen.dk
SSLType IMAPS
SSLVersions TLSv1.2
PassCmd "gpg --quiet --for-your-eyes-only --no-tty --decrypt ~/.mutt/one.com.gpg"
CertificateFile ~/.mutt/imap.one.com.pem

# Remote storage
IMAPStore one-remote
Account one

# Local storage
MaildirStore one-local
Path ~/Mail/one/
Inbox ~/Mail/one/INBOX
SubFolders Verbatim

Channel one-inbox
Master :one-remote:
Slave :one-local:
Patterns *
SyncState *
Create Both
Expunge Both
CopyArrivalDate Yes

Group one
Channel one-inbox

